&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;n509o3&quot; data-start=&quot;649&quot; data-end=&quot;770&quot;&gt;Provide technical and engineering support in the exploitation of commercial network infrastructure and computer systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1evr404&quot; data-start=&quot;771&quot; data-end=&quot;850&quot;&gt;Support the research and development of tools and new concepts for operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
