&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;yprcwk&quot; data-start=&quot;1011&quot; data-end=&quot;1066&quot;&gt;Wide range of scripting skills across Bash and Python&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1j1n7k0&quot; data-start=&quot;1067&quot; data-end=&quot;1157&quot;&gt;Strong critical thinking skills, communication skills, and ability to work independently&lt;/li&gt;
