&lt;li&gt;Perform internal and external penetration testing across multiple operational environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Simulate cyber and RF-enabled attack vectors against mission systems and communications architectures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify security weaknesses, exploit vulnerabilities, and demonstrate potential operational and business impacts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct social engineering, phishing, and physical security assessments where authorized.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RF, Space, and Mission Systems Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
